ABSTRACT

Trendsetter is a modern clothing boutique located in Bengaluru that offers casual wear, formal wear, western fashion, and ethnic wear for women, men, and children.

This project focuses on developing an AI-generated UGC Ad Content Pack using structured prompts and prompt engineering techniques. The content was designed for multiple social media platforms including Instagram Reels, TikTok, and YouTube Shorts.

The advertisements emphasize Trendsetter’s key strengths including trendy collections, affordable pricing, quality products, and handmade designs while maintaining authentic customer-focused storytelling.

INTRODUCTION

In today's digital marketing landscape, consumers increasingly trust authentic customer experiences over traditional advertisements.

User-Generated Content (UGC) has become one of the most effective marketing approaches because it creates trust, relatability, and engagement.

This project demonstrates how AI-powered prompt engineering can be used to generate platform-specific UGC advertisements that showcase fashion products while maintaining authenticity and audience appeal.

PROBLEM STATEMENT

Fashion boutiques often face challenges in creating engaging social media content consistently across multiple platforms.

Traditional content creation requires significant time, creativity, and marketing expertise.

There is a growing need for efficient methods that can generate high-quality promotional content while maintaining brand identity and audience engagement.

AI-powered prompt engineering provides a solution by enabling the rapid creation of customized UGC advertisements for different platforms and audiences.

